content:
dheaton-arm opened PR #4508 from isle-fpops to main:

Converted the existing implementations for the following opcodes to ISLE
on AArch64:

  • sqrt
  • fneg
  • fabs
  • fpromote
  • fdemote
  • ceil
  • floor
  • trunc
  • nearest
